  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Waiting to go to sea",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, sea areas off the coast from Colombo to Pottuvil via Galle and Hambantota may be rough.",
        "The warning notice issued by the department also states that this warning is valid until 2.00 pm tomorrow (19).",
        "The department states that the people engaged in fishing and marine activities in that sea area should be alert as fast winds of 50, 60 km per hour can occur in those sea areas."
      ],
